.slds-notify_container
  ngl-toast(*ngIf="showTopToast", variant="error", (close)="onClose($event); showTopToast = false;", duration="5000")
    h2.slds-text-heading_small This error will automatically hide after 5 seconds if you don't click on the close button
|
ngl-toast(iconName="utility:info")
  h2.slds-text-heading_small
    | This is a toast with an icon next to its
    |
    a(href="javascript:void(0);") message
    |.
  p Here's some detail of what happened...
|
button.slds-m-top_medium(type="button", [disabled]="showTopToast", nglButton="neutral", (click)="showTopToast = true")
  | Show toast in container
